  "overview": "El Cajon PD ( CA) uses Flock Safety technology to capture objective evidence without compromising on individual privacy. El Cajon PD utilizes retroactive searches to solve crimes after they've occurred. Additionally, El Cajon PD utilizes real-time alerting of hotlist vehicles to capture wanted criminals.",
